data.description: LISTED UNDER APPRAISED VALUE! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style at 2625 Tuscarora Ct. This charming 4-bed, 3-bath home welcomes you with a NEW roof and fresh paint. Bright and airy living spaces complement the modern kitchen with an island, creating an inviting atmosphere. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in the spacious backyard with a stunning view of the pond, offering tranquility and a touch of nature. The fenced-in backyard, complete with dual 6' gates, provides privacy and security. Conveniently located in a sought-after gated neighborhood, this residence offers both serenity and accessibility. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
